snippet.title: Indians In Summer Vacation | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys ,
This Video all the things that happen in summer vacations . Every Indian in summer vacations going on vacation with family to hill stations like shimla , manali , mussoorie , darjeeling , haridwar , rishikesh . Indian moms dealing with holiday homework given by school teachers during summer break , Family trips , horse ridding , trekking , hiking . watching sunsets , sunrise at famous hill tops , creating memories clicking pictures , tourist locations and rush of people and traffic jams , mother excited to go vacation getting her beauty regime by parlour didi , waxing , facial , threading , bleach , dtan , shopping from sarojini nagar to travel , buying gifts for relatives on vacay , travelling by train enjoying , singing eating train food , road trip with family , stopping at dhaba , mom feeding her home cooked food puri aloo jeera sabzi , middle class dad driving on highway , kids singing fighting taking pictures on the way to himachal and so much more ..
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family especially guests .. Comment down your Fav Part, 
Like, Share and

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: वित्त मंत्री निर्मला सीतारमण के दामाद कौन हैं?
snippet.description:
#nirmalasitharaman #soninlaw #financeministry #finance #pratikdoshi #marriage #wedding #parakalavangmayi #pratikdoshi
देश की वित्त मंत्री निर्मला सीतारमण की बेटी शादी के बंधन में बंध गई हैं। ऐसे में आपको मन में कई तरह के सवाल उठ रहे होंगे कि वित्त मंत्री की बेटी कौन हैं? किससे उनकी शादी हुई है यानि कि उनके दामाद कौन हैं? इसके साथ ही वित्त मंत्री की बेटी की शादियों में कौन-कौन सी हस्तियां शामिल हुईं? जानने के लिए देखिए ये वीडियो

बिजनेस जगत की हर बड़ी खबर, उनसे जुड़े एक्सप्लेनर वीडियो, बिजनेस शख्सियत  की दिलचस्प कहानियां, रियल एस्टेट, गोल्ड, ऑटो सेक्टर, स्टार्टअप्स,  शेयर बाजार, सेंसेक्स और पर्सलन फाइनेंस जैसे विषयों की जानकारी हासिल करने के लिए जुड़े बिजनेस टुडे हिंदी से। यहां आपकों म्यूचुअल फंड, एसआईपी, इक्विटी, बीमा, लोन्स, पेंशन, रिटायरमेंट योजनाओं के बारे में आसान भाषा में मिलेगी दिलचस्प जानकारी।

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: bye, from Dream.
snippet.description:
bye, from Dream. I deleted my face reveal, and this is why.

After face revealing and removing my mask, I regretted the attention and hate, and am walking it back.


Pre-save Until I End Up Dead: https://presave.umusic.com/dream

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dream
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

I will slowly be deleting all pictures of me online, and going back to just being a gamer in a mask. Starting with my Mr Beast Video, and my Face Reveal video, "hi, I'm Dream". I will be walking it back. I will be getting rid of everything other than my new mask.

The same company that made the spider man mask, batman mask, and many other superheroes, made me a mask so that I can be Dream all of the time. Hide my identity, even if public, at McDonalds, or any place I need to go.

thank you all from the bottom of my heart to those that supported me, even though I am ugly. I appreciate you all more than you could ever know, and I will be working on my face while I'm masked again.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 53 Teaser - 8th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 53 Teaser - 8th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Tere Bin Episode 52 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 8th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq

snippet.title: Jhoom Episode 10 Teaser - 9th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Jhoom Episode 10 Teaser - 9th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

A journey of JHOOM into the world of love, relationships, heartbreak, and sacrifice that centers around the lives of two souls who find love in a world of chaos and uncertainty that changes their lives forever. Aryaan is a young and handsome boy who holds a caring and possessive nature towards his friends. Despite having a traumatic past, Aryaan tries to smile through the worries of life and never steps back from helping his friends.

However, Aryaan's life takes an unexpected turn when he meets Maryam, a compassionate and kind-hearted woman who becomes a ray of sunshine in his life. As their relationship begin to flourish, Aryaan feels a change in himself and embraces the love that he had been deprived for so long.

Despite the significant age gap between them, Aryaan and Maryam's love for each other knows no bounds, and they embark on an unconventional journey together. Their love defies societal norms and expectations, challenging the prejudices and biases of those around them.

As their relationship progresses, their love is put to the ultimate test. Will they be able to overcome their challenges and sacrifices to stay together? Will their love stand the test of time and societal pressure? Is age just a number when it comes to love?

Written By: Hashim Nadeem
Directed By: Ali Faizan
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3793 | 9 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3793: 6 Baje Wali Samasya
--------------------------------------------------------
Kalpana chooses to engrave a tattoo for Pyaarelal, putting him in an awkward position. Meanwhile, Kalpana and Sapna have both requested that Pyaarelal meet them at 6 p.m. at the same spot. Pyaarelal seeks assistance from his sisters, the Gokuldham ladies, out of uncertainty. Anjali then summons Taarak to assist her in making the best decision for Pyaarelal. When Taarak phones Jetha for recommendations, Jetha and Bagha at Gada Electronics decide to throw a samosa party. Jetha invites Taarak to eat the samosas, unknowing that Anjali is on the queue. Will Taarak be caught red-handed in his hidden fast-food binge? Pyaarelal's encounters with both females will be difficult to handle. Keep an eye out!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3793, 9 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3794: Yellow Or Blue?
--------------------------------------------------------
Both Kalpana and Sapna have asked Pyaarelal to meet them at the same location at 6 o'clock. While Pyaarelal is out with Kalpana, he visits Sapna in different clothes. Police keep a watch on Pyaarelal because of his questionable behavior as he has been running and visiting two ladies at the same time by changing clothes inside a truck. Pyarelal eats ice cream and gol gape with Kalpana and Sapna in order to know more about them. Later, the police confront Sapna and show her Pyarelaal's activities with Kalpana. Keep an eye out!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: മരണത്തിന് തൊട്ട്മുൻപ് വേദിയിൽ തമാശ പറഞ്ഞും പൊട്ടി ചിരിച്ചും സുധി ബിനു അടിമാലിക്കൊപ്പം | Kollam Sudhi
snippet.description:
Comedian Kollam Sudhi's car collided with a pickup van at Kaipamangalam in Thrissur while returning to Kochi after participating in a stage show in Vadakara, Kozhikode.

കോഴിക്കോട് വടകരയിൽ നടന്ന 24 കണക്ടിന്റെ സ്റ്റേജ് ഷോയിൽ പങ്കെടുത്ത് തിരികെ കൊച്ചിയിലേക്ക് മടങ്ങും വഴിയായിരുന്നു ഹാസ്യതാരം കൊല്ലം സുധി സഞ്ചരിച്ചിരുന്ന കാർ തൃശ്ശൂർ കൈപ്പമംഗലത്ത് വച്ച് വാഹനം പിക്കപ്പ് വാനുമായി കൂട്ടിയിടിക്കുന്നത്. | Kollam sudhi Death

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3792: Bohot Sara Khaana
--------------------------------------------------------
After Kalpana's departure, Sapna arrives at the same restaurant. Pyaarelal greets Sapna with the same flower that Kalpana had given him. Sapna shows her romantic gestures, and she holds Pyaarelal's hands, which makes him ecstatic. Anjali makes a fake call from Pyaarelal's office, Toofan Express, and tells him to report immediately. Sapna gets upset about Pyaarelal's departure, so she requests that he meet her again at 6 p.m. Pyaarelal changes his attire to blue because this time he will be visiting Kalpana again. So Pyaarelal changes his outfit in the car. When Pyaarelal reaches Sapna's place, Anjali and Komal have already arrived. How will Pyaarelal juggle his double life now? Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3792, 8 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: Jetha ने क्यों दी Bagha और Nattu Kaka को Party? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Jetha Chala US
snippet.description:
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Jetha has to leave for America in next three days. Bagha and Nattu Kaka celebrate this and ask Jetha to give them a party. Jetha orders Pizza and French fries for them. He calls Bapuji to tell the news but Nattu Kaka stops him from doing so. Jetha thinks he had such a good day just because of Babita Ji as she told him have a nice day. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 3547
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of 'Bhide Bana Crorepati':
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSCH5ciwJoKjs1SCjN150tq

snippet.description:
सरिताज किचनची सर्व उत्पादने शुद्ध, पारंपरिक आणि केमिकल विरहित आहेत.

वर्षभर टिकणारे कैरीचे लोणचे | ५ आणि १ किलोच्या परफेक्ट प्रमाणात सविस्तर कृती Kairiche Lonache Recipe
कैरीचे लोणचे, एकदाच करून ठेवले तर अगदी २ वर्षे आरामात टिकते. पण आजकाल कैरी लोणचे करताना लहान सहान गोष्टी माहिती नसल्याने, लोणचे करतो अगदी छान पण लगेच बुरशी येणे, खराब होणे असे प्रॉब्लेम्स होतात. किंवा लोणच्याला आंबूस, पुंगस वास येतो. तर आज आपण अगदी पारंपरिक पद्धतीने आजीच्या बटव्यातील टिप्स वापरून हे लोणचे बनवणार आहोत.
लोणचे करताना कैरी कोणती वापरावी? आंब्याचे लोणचे करतांना कोणती काळजी घ्यावी? जेणेकरून ते खराब होणार नाही, तसेच मसाले वा त्याचे अगदी योग्य प्रमाण दिले आहे. त्यामुळे लोणच्याची चव अप्रतिम चटपटीत येईल पण त्याचबरोबर ते अगदी २ वर्षे म्हंटले तरी आरामात टिकेल.  

कैरीचं तिखट गोड लोणचं | कैरीचें लोणचे | आंब्याचे लोणचे | आंबट गोड कैरीचे लोणचे | खान्देश स्पेशल आंब्याचे गुळातले लोणचे | Spicy Sweet Mango Pickle | Ambyache Lonche | Kairiche Gulache Lonache Recipe | Lonache recipe Marathi | Ambyache Lonache 

साहित्य | Ingredients 
 • कैरी 5 किलो | Raw Mango (which we use for pickle) 5 kg
 • हळद १०० ग्राम | Turmeric 100 gram
 • खडे मीठ ५०० ग्राम | Rock Salt 500 gram
घरगुती मसाल्यासाठी | For Masala 
 • हिंग खडे 25-30 gram | Asafoetida 25to 30 gram|
 • मेथ्या ५० ग्राम | Fenugreek Seeds 50 gram
 • दालचिनी 7-8 इंच | Cinnamon 7-8 inch
 • लवंग १ मोठा चमचा 5-6 gram  | Cloves 1 tbsp (5-6gram)
 • काली मिरी १ मोठा चमचा (6 -7 grams) | Black pepper corns 1 tbsp ( 6-7 grams)
 
 • तेल सव्वा किलो | Oil 1 & 1/4 kilo
 • मोहरीची डाळ ५०० ग्राम |Split Mustered Yellow 500 gram
 • मिरची पावडर २५० ग्राम | Red Chilly pw 250 gram 
 • हळद १०० ग्राम | Turmeric 100 gram
 • मीठ ३००  ग्राम | Salt 300 gram
 • तयार लोणचे मसाला ५०० ग्राम | Readymade Pickle Masala 500 Gram
 • बारीक चिरलेला गुळ दीड किलो | Chopped Jaggery 1.5 kg

१ किलो कैरीसाठी प्रमाण | Measurements for 1 kilo Mangoes
कैरी 1 किलो | Raw Mango (which we use for pickle) 1 kg
 • हळद 20 ग्राम | Turmeric 20 gram
 • खडे मीठ 100 ग्राम | Rock Salt 100 gram
घरगुती मसाल्यासाठी | For Masala 
 • हिंग खडे 5-6 gram | Asafoetida 5-6 gram|
 • मेथ्या 10 ग्राम | Fenugreek Seeds 10 gram
 • दालचिनी 2-3 इंच | Cinnamon 2-3 inch
 • लवंग १०-१२    | Cloves 10-12 
 • काली मिरी १०-१२  Black pepper corns १०-१२  
 
 • तेल पाव  किलो | Oil 250 grams 
 • मोहरीची डाळ 100 ग्राम |Split Mustered Yellow 100 gram
 • मिरची पावडर 50 ग्राम | Red Chilly pw 50 gram 
 • हळद 20 ग्राम | Turmeric 20 gram
 • मीठ 75  ग्राम | Salt 75 gram
 • तयार लोणचे मसाला 100 ग्राम | Readymade Pickle Masala 100 Gram
 • बारीक चिरलेला गुळ 250 gram | Chopped Jaggery 250 gram

snippet.description:
Subscribe To Shemaroo Movie in Parts: https://www.youtube.com/user/shemaroopremiumfilms?sub_confirmation=1

Orphaned at a very young age, Raju lives a poor lifestyle with his unmarried sister, Laxmi, in India. Both are of marriageable age. One day Raju meets an attractive fellow-collegian, Parul, and after a few encounters with another fellow-collegian, Bobby, both fall in love. But Parul's uncle, Jagpal, has already arranged her marriage with Police Inspector Suryadev Singh. When Suryadev finds out that Parul is refusing to marry him, he arrests Raju on a charge of murder, holds him in a cell, and beats him mercilessly.

Laxmi, quite dramatically, takes a gun from a police officer, and helps Raju escape so as to prevent Parul from being forcibly married to Suryadev. They do manage to arrive in time, only to find out that Parul has consumed poison and killed herself. Raju is beside himself with rage, but is captured by the police, and watches helplessly as Parul is cremated. His horrors have not ended as Suryadev sexually assault's Laxmi and leaves her in a mentally unstable condition.

Directed by K. Ravi Shankar
Written by Satish Jain
Story by Su. Thirunavukkarasar
Produced by A. Krishnamurthy
Starring - Govinda, Shilpa Shetty, Sonali Bendre
Cinematography K. V. Ramanna
Music by Dilip Sen-Sameer Sen

लक्ष्मी, काफी नाटकीय रूप से, एक पुलिस अधिकारी से बंदूक लेती है, और राजू को भागने में मदद करती है ताकि पारुल को सूर्यदेव से जबरन शादी करने से रोका जा सके। वे समय पर पहुंचने का प्रबंधन करते हैं, केवल यह पता लगाने के लिए कि पारुल ने जहर खा लिया है और खुद को मार डाला है। राजू गुस्से में खुद के बगल में है, लेकिन पुलिस द्वारा कब्जा कर लिया जाता है, और पारुल का अंतिम संस्कार करते हुए बेबसी से देखता है। उसकी भयावहता समाप्त नहीं हुई है क्योंकि सूर्यदेव ने लक्ष्मी का यौन उत्पीड़न किया और उसे मानसिक रूप से अस्थिर स्थिति में छोड़ दिया।
